ActExport and Import Permits Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Export Control List
PrecisOrder Amending the EXPORT CONTROL LIST in order to add certain Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement (CETA) export Origin Quota-eligible goods to the Export Control List in order for the Government of Canada to establish export permit requirements for these goods.
